				<td class="PanelBodyAlternate"><span class="SmallBoldText">Re: Shielding % Mods...weaker than advertised, or broken?<a name="47324"/></span><br><span class="SmallText"> Posted: </span><span class="SmallText">Jun 21 04 11:37 AM</span></td>
			</tr><tr>
				<td colspan="2"><span>Go to the steel warrior board for best information on shielding. The damage you take from a mobs melee is based on a damage bonus and a damage interval. Shielding only works against the DB  (defensive works on the DI).  Mobs can have very different DB and DI values.
<br />

<br />
damage = DB + DI *(rand20)
<br />

<br />

<br />

<br />

<br />

<br />

<br />
edited: slight mod on wording</span></td>
